OL,5,G1250 All Creatures Great and Small
OL,6,     FWhen a familiar face from Helen's
OL,7,     Fpast returns to Darrowby, James
OL,8,     Fworries that he must vie for her
OL,9,     Fattention and steps up to compete
OL,10,     Fat Mrs Pumphrey's annual cricket
OL,11,     Fmatch.
OL,12,G1350 All Creatures Great and Small
OL,13,     FTristan remains at a crossroads,
OL,14,     Fbut when Mrs Donovan's dog ends up
OL,15,     Fin an accident, he learns a
OL,16,     Fvaluable lesson which helps him
OL,17,     Fmake a decision about his future.
