OL,5,G1455 All Creatures Great and Small
OL,6,     FAfter an eventful second series on
OL,7,     Fthe Yorkshire Dales, All Creatures
OL,8,     FGreat and Small returns with a
OL,9,     Fspecial episode, as James and
OL,10,     FHelen spend their first Christmas
OL,11,     Ftogether.
OL,12,G1600 All Creatures Great and Small
OL,13,     FBig changes are happening at
OL,14,     FSkeldale, and everyone has to
OL,15,     Flearn how to adjust. Tristan is
OL,16,     Fnow a qualified vet, while James
OL,17,     Fenters a new stage of his life
OL,18,     Fwith Helen and the practice.
